    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014it still has that new-car feel and has been babied since day one. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. It drives like an absolute dream! If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
